  "text": "Berries have been commercialized as fresh or frozen whole fruits, freeze-dried berries, puree, juice, or wine [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Although most processing methods cause a significant decrease in the anthocyanin content [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] , freeze-drying has been reported to cause the least reduction in total polyphenol content of berries [CITATION_7] .",
